Package de.dfki.omm.interfaces

Interfaces describing structure and functionality of various implementing classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BinaryCodec
    Binary en- and decryption of a payload.
    JSONOutput
    Interface for objects that need to present themselves as JSON objects or JSON Strings in order to output OMS contents.
    OMM
    Represents an instance of the OMM (object memory model).
    OMMAttributeListBlock
    Contains all information of a OMM attribute list block.
    OMMBlock
    Contains all meta data information of a OMM block.
    OMMHeader
    Contains all information of a OMM header.
    OMMIdentifierBlock
    Contains all information of an OMM identification block.
    OMMRestInterface
    Interface for RESTful representations of OMMs, controlling cached data and access modes.
    OMMSemanticsBlock
    Contains all information of a OMM semantics block.
    OMMStorage  
    OMMStructureBlock
    Contains all information of a OMM structure block.
    OMMToCEntry
    Contains all meta data information of a OMM table of contents entry.

Package de.dfki.omm.interfaces Description

Interfaces describing structure and functionality of various implementing classes.
